20" rel="nofollow" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1148994&amp;amp;li=17995347&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=05052026221045&amp;amp;lctg=8b37da73-f2d1-4a1c-8a9f-cb9d10343de6&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=mobile&amp;amp;collapse_width=550" style="display: block !important; width: 100% !important;" width="550" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;!--&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;人工智能宠儿 Anthropic 推出了一系列新的人工智能代理，它们直接针对华尔街。 Anthropic 旨在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/7OQyqYBDxHiCH5bU8VLLwQLpJp1ejL3OuTc2hD_BbidT6PZqBiiY0ux6rmYOyRn3CE3xvLSydAL06__nltBMSIw1OrxIRpgj_dLfiu0gAlik32n5vI4cQbgj2oT_b6UcG_ZYvQCVQ9JvBHPFD0z-fng3ZK3W1IxuJY7gCZzKOEkjr_ucSO0KsYWGfVaCg8AHRMeDQ71PZZhD-eeEuUMTGEnuOXu-FSlP4Ix2bQijt6oY-wt2MomowLp6ppoUFo8CMLdBaySjEUJjDcckLU3_zaE762Gc78TNHMlpxpBNLO5_t7Igh7xyvlG-Zeom6ft64jMaBXJ8unebA2Q0DluBY6zKSMC02l0kQX_hu3d2lvbc4784f9daN1UzoqqqNqGQOgpILdgfGH3b-gKx01Cr00hUlATzDD3-JHu9R-N_bNDFf5y3fRSiAfyZMJa-NHAXjQcZsK9Ch6q36HBYPw9BiWtigLw0NpPMF31dwKjdfnOJVnLv21S2-fwncVVeZIXR6W3Lrn-JpvQG1qD1GMes1i1zek4/o7GoBG2I-v_z3gaQGxPfzjT-1G1zBEZO/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="Anthropic 推出人工智能代理来执行金融服务任务"&gt;处理更广泛的金融服务任务&lt;/a&gt;，表示他们可以为客户会议起草宣传材料、审查财务报表以及升级合规审查案例。这些新工具共有 10 个，直接针对银行、保险、资产管理和金融技术领域的专业人士。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;今年 2 月，Anthropic 的一款自动化工具&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/I3XmTChJzB8aXM1_IXRcoI9_IxzjIezFvt3lNpYIWtwDkfTIbxtIaaHW8NrBCQ_BXcUqaVvM5rTA8Gz2yiBCDDmjiUfW2O3DNUKubSJTf6iTy2MbwwHOPOdcCtsJEf-gNxFDnw03f77HVwkU3j_ZJQVPmKdTy7U4FqeeYZi8VSlOyhbKV-YajLlWQ0VAugLapUtOGcnv2G0vdhNf9ezbpDmYwwpoc4fkHK8-eWZJSgXo15ceSHA-xQbWpCf9GpQGpHonPDrzcAOU3BtVhLCLhweJYk96TmIYuiyAQZ4hAnCOhiM7zSV9SNFjZuEV030Ua1RntWZeE2xE2aOmGTZzBza5P8tIKuTDrbgTZJmn4CWxjUGo45T1ebCWpDVBJs2Ck3f77bDBdvAHKxeTh