ASs7zrYKS7ZuSBSnnpxn3pQb0EKxoyazaTFy2CenNn0SLK2UV8Esc5Y_JcP6MwtvVqM3eXKCQoiPfU0qGS47DBfKtvb1OwZPxFnr4Wi9Q_CPt90DdVsqX2WL_xUg/-KK6nGZlH7PoOsLbowOMXN8WyOF41I4W/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="德鲁·辛德尔"&gt;德鲁·辛德尔&lt;/a&gt;表示，他们的实验通过精确测量不同颜色颗粒吸收阳光的速度开辟了新天地。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;他说，大气中的塑料颗粒要么已经是黑色的，要么是较浅的塑料颗粒随着年龄的增长而变暗。 “最终的影响是变暖，”辛德尔说。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/BLbWvtN4vCrRz-1z1b6WdUOZ-BT36aH7lCIF2NuZqu8GAWXslY-7UF5LLCk9ZfwIA-WVdAQE_aQTbQxkRUkScK8A7enrSn30YjvduHFyR5jfr_DxfH6t74eBcolqXIro0KQ6LuJFTO5q5wRvxrQpIup21o4AcdWgq2mQlf5tWr32ogma2qxAMJIbv06lHPuCl3TpI5OphUzk6UQ76GBUbVMh30sB6DDqhzL8vfcTm4j3GvKdYfwo_MIdujI44ROEDrLYEL0f2e8LB4whE2qP68lyjsm5hthAQXAAS3GhdGsmUPdqkuD85XU6EKAsyih5FiT4lwd9J8WClwmYM5V8tF0Iar73d1eKSZLBDg2HeeAfAMfVQ_1EF41zFsL6YQczdrDLbkIfMdNgdVywTCV3WEvcRm1CIqiFtC8VlIX56oljKmso4V6GcfZqL-UzvmC-9XI6sS0pWpQgfo_L01SLoDPHN94pVyTeGIl2MyYVLW8V1QSMrb9tQdxv2CPQ_3jndU8KD1lUykKWpqS2OqTMTPLNHBFnO-bVavrimQa7ZkMc8O5yV9GZk2xylg/Cik8jSWZXawak_isZu7jhtLh7azHU-dP/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e; text-decoration: none !important;" target="_blank" title="研究发现吸热微塑料在气候变化中发挥作用"&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; margin: 24px 0 0 0; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; font-size: 14px !important; color: #000 !important; text-decoration: none !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 20px;" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" style="padding: 0;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/GHleJYpNy0uYhNFXFUffcEZQxBnM023qO_dVDHXa7JAcRDmD5L3-MOVxRmYt3l4Ho_h3Ab6BXsiBicJI2zQGruxdfKZY-zA1vOZgcnIeL3J2oUqRa7F9dFeFo9yhyYGElyzAgtzSLBDzHfmb4QoAcAOuaeX94ClJUsoB0EQqPpy-ds1eT1EC3Y6IT12njf1lVSAgZMS3sW71ClICcOvgA1W0TEoNdv4hOU6guKS43kEuFhxDHNk4X3jBBh_s8CpTRyEmll4uZ