top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;高市的澳大利亚之行展示了两国的“准联盟”——实际上&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/f4Gn3cdjN8Mn3duSv3rjeBvtZS3vp6E6jaORl7tdsyl6ifOH_qffapAytrq7NN4-PAU-rz9ppAIYrcEuHrfIwITSJaH2wt9fVlP5FfgbGqBxaZfZk_E6-0qFMQDD8qyEQr6wicN0WtKFGzGf5_5Qq8rCYA3ks5vVy7S6t6S56waeIcfBQjGw4W9T8kPNB0KAD4c6SImvY0QXtkVE95iSXFkRXRnS7y8jyPERrbpNL21jygRNciZsOtFxWIiMhdqHMnlnUCkCb5Vjli86GrdcNWjjY41oyW_Vbl04Ajur7aEPvSb5hrBlnZQX9NgerDwvI_THAouJgQ_3D-LahSAvxkF9-BZxoKHpfoNgMvx9JHDfuBvqiM5IPw1bnfQI8vCK5kp369rqU2Y-cW95TgaOK361GH9IKgP7fsgw4q39e1QbcrJ_tHy4PtZfLr3MACMLhhP6wmun9I89Gy6EfTo_clNwNNeKBDDCoOaqADXOWiShmuEs_GpljvSz38V2C8atIfSx1G4gO0kTMTVthzIXbewZfzFu8-87duiJeSFob8_1Lg/_w940k_yVRH_Ro_joZzlvSqhuZDvYELW/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="日本高市在演讲中阐述了新的印太愿景"&gt;是继美国之后两国最好的合作伙伴&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;在堪培拉，她可以轻松地谈论自己的爱好：重金属。首相安东尼·艾博尼斯 (Anthony Albanese) 也是一位摇滚乐迷，高市送给他一个唱片柜。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;黑胶唱片中有一张名为&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;《世界着火》的&lt;/em&gt;专辑。&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;—&lt;/em&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/GuftNpP-FdNqBOV1_YQpp29rvCfJwpex_51zDFbaRnOroaFo6B6HDc4HUvq_BHIPTRNGemVo77m1zOdz9baWcuoNZab780Z2gWU0x3PBrAf7B9ndDCoRpctNM2P9WIlPybhBvfNIUfT0LQdqr1pd0g96K-6PGG84MtsfTs77kIOV9_a05zgWFwRx0z2xeLgUIXqrGoyamMTEJkSxmGol8ROvQ2gq7bbk6CaCwqL8b-w1EAtHgdPrpYhU78Indah1VX_kkOi0ZVc8ytj27-4aTiL04oEI0-8JFUQdumAq4M3BDvAMP7jl-A6kqyIUfJA5I7LRbXvUqEPK/CEkPbEZLIdX4hpXreP8awyNhviIW3P4-/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="横山艾丽卡 |布隆伯格"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;埃里卡·横山&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;和&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/p0u_vT-6BLaFMqRlc6QqzPhoAbyWUbQAN8FOKSFfBtF5Hk8bUbGRR9zXMxix3442qbyYUVRkzlsp-c3a3m40Ov5bIQ-K3KzEKKKFt2h-jHIfF