 petition has been started by separatist activists in Alberta for a referendum on independence from Canada, driven in part by a belief that the government in Ottawa hasn’t done enough to accelerate projects to expand oil production, such as new pipelines. Photographer: Leah Hennel&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2026 年 1 月 26 日星期一，与会者抵达加拿大阿尔伯塔省卡尔加里参加阿尔伯塔独立市政厅活动。阿尔伯塔省的分离主义活动人士已发起请愿书，要求就从加拿大独立进行公投，部分原因是渥太华政府在加快扩大石油产量的项目（例如新管道）方面做得不够。摄影师：Leah Hennel&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iWPd.FYOvjF8/v9/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt; 1 月 26 日，一名参与者抵达卡尔加里参加阿尔伯塔独立市政厅活动。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：Leah Hennel/彭博社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;更多来自彭博社&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul style="margin-top: 24px; padding-inline-start: 24px;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16px;"&gt;观看我们的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/FoFNjwrb39WknIhZ1NV_iXrevoCP-uuJF9Nnm-R47nFz-ZlY1lyCWBSAVeTDyli3EyvdiiSB07iH91RsgefPc0LxTedK1OLF4ZGI7pWPdietqdHsGbtleFjNYjQ7PkZ2iS6V1o0k5nOn1GtRwCntMIZC0k0DX3QDCAvW-huD_6DSHl5zgErGacS4tMiuk3GIKHiMzO5njLSasllYXTcWGiTgZ-Zi-XKwGghaExGyTzB-OiIARg0ht_KSdEC5TbVD0HfuLynTQX7DHyTGMJs-K-Xdvy5D7TFMQ1JclaAajb8dciEGoTGIPPN9cd6Ryz-JTwnYNr9fPJr1KuniO6JsBE2Pv_XYW__1zi7Cyw/ZQQEYdFhY7KX_F0IzH7hrmiiAvswCu1c/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: 16px;" target="_blank"&gt;彭博调查&lt;/a&gt;电影系列，了解不为人知的故事和未解之谜&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 16